Q. Create a small calculator which only does ‘+’ or ‘-‘OperaƟons. (Hint: Take three variable inputs with
one being used for the operator)
START
INPUT num1
INPUT operator
INPUT num2
IF operator == “+” THEN
.	PRINT(num1 + num2)
ELSEIF operator == “-” THEN
.	PRINT(num1 - num2)
ELSE
PRINT “function not available”
END
